d:
看似弱不经风的外表下
却是刚劲有力的每一次起舞
勾魂摄魄的平衡力
随舞而动的情绪感
“菟丝花是对为你起舞的我，最大的误解”
彼之良·青棠【噗叽小蛋糕/仿生2.2CF系列/155Mcm】

Underneath the seemingly weak appearance,
it is the strength and power of every dance.
A balance that captivates the senses,
a sense of emotion that moves with the dance.
Cuscuta is the biggest misunderstanding of me who dancing for you.
Bezlya Albizia PuffieCakie, Bionic 2.2 CF series 155cm M ver
